information: The company ÖSTERREICHISCHE GENOSSENSCHAFT DES LANDWIRTSCHAFTLICHEN ERWERBSGARTENBAUES REGISTRIERTE GE, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1949, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It is based in Wien, Austria.
